  "description": "<p><strong>Healthcare Agency looking for passionate individual to join us as HR Intern</strong></p><ul><li>General HR administrative documentation</li><li>Assist the recruitment process for healthcare personnel</li><li>Manage and develop Social Media recruitment drive</li><li>Basic Documentation</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Singaporeans Only</li><li>Training will be provided</li><li>Candidates with no experiences are welcomed to apply</li><li>Good communication and interpersonal skill</li><li>Able to work independently</li><li>Proficient in MS Office</li><li>3 to 6 month contract</li><li> January 2026 onward</li></ul><p>Interested applicants please email your detailed resume to mycareer@abercare.sg</p><p><br /></p><p>Abercare.sg | EA License No. 18C9070 | KOH SU WEN, CLARISSA| Registration No. R24119504</p>",
